{"name": "nonebot-plugin-pingti", "metadata": {"name": "nonebot-plugin-pingti", "version": "0.2.0", "classifiers": [], "home_page": null, "license": "MIT", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["nonebot2", "nonebot-plugin-alconna", "nonebot-plugin-waiter", "httpx"], "summary": "Shop with lower prices by searching with alternative keywords.", "upload_time": 1733735008}, "documentation": ["<!-- markdownlint-disable MD031 MD033 MD036 MD041 -->\n\n<div align=\"center\">\n\n<a href=\"https://v2.nonebot.dev/store\">\n  <img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/A-kirami/nonebot-plugin-template/resources/nbp_logo.png\" width=\"180\" height=\"180\" alt=\"NoneBotPluginLogo\">\n</a>\n\n<p>\n  <img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/lgc-NB2Dev/readme/main/template/plugin.svg\" alt=\"NoneBotPluginText\">\n</p>\n\n# NoneBot-Plugin-PingTi\n\n_\u2728 \u8ba9 AI \u5e2e\u4f60\u5bfb\u627e\u66f4\u4f4e\u4ef7\u7684\u8d2d\u7269\u641c\u7d22\u8bcd \u2728_\n\n<img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/python-3.9+-blue.svg\" alt=\"python\">\n<a href=\"https://pdm.fming.dev\">\n  <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/pdm-managed-blueviolet\" alt=\"pdm-managed\">\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://wakatime.com/badge/user/b61b0f9a-f40b-4c82-bc51-0a75c67bfccf/project/018cef6a-03d4-4902-8b19-272f441456ef\">\n  <img src=\"https://wakatime.com/badge/user/b61b0f9a-f40b-4c82-bc51-0a75c67bfccf/project/018cef6a-03d4-4902-8b19-272f441456ef.svg\" alt=\"wakatime\">\n</a>\n\n<br />\n\n<a href=\"https://pydantic.dev\">\n  <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/endpoint?url=https://raw.githubusercontent.com/lgc-NB2Dev/readme/main/template/pyd-v1-or-v2.json\" alt=\"Pydantic Version 1 Or 2\" >\n</a>\n<a href=\"./LICENSE\">\n  <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/github/license/lgc-NB2Dev/nonebot-plugin-pingti.svg\" alt=\"license\">\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://pypi.python.org/pypi/nonebot-plugin-pingti\">\n  <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/nonebot-plugin-pingti.svg\" alt=\"pypi\">\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://pypi.python.org/pypi/nonebot-plugin-pingti\">\n  <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/pypi/dm/nonebot-plugin-pingti\" alt=\"pypi download\">\n</a>\n\n<br />\n\n<a href=\"https://registry.nonebot.dev/plugin/nonebot-plugin-pingti:nonebot_plugin_pingti\">\n  <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/endpoint?url=https%3A%2F%2Fnbbdg.lgc2333.top%2Fplugin%2Fnonebot-plugin-pingti\" alt=\"NoneBot Registry\">\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://registry.nonebot.dev/plugin/nonebot-plugin-pingti:nonebot_plugin_pingti\">\n  <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/endpoint?url=https%3A%2F%2Fnbbdg.lgc2333.top%2Fplugin-adapters%2Fnonebot-plugin-pingti\" alt=\"Supported Adapters\">\n</a>\n\n</div>\n\n## \ud83d\udcd6 \u7b80\u4ecb\n\n\u8282\u9009\u81ea[\u539f\u7f51\u7ad9](https://www.pingti.xyz/)\uff1a\n\n> \u540c\u4e00\u4ef6\u5546\u54c1\uff0c\u4e0d\u540c\u7684\u641c\u7d22\u8bcd\uff0c\u4ef7\u683c\u53ef\u80fd\u4f1a\u5929\u5dee\u5730\u522b\u3002  \n> \u8fd9\u4e2a\u5de5\u5177\u65e8\u5728\u5e2e\u52a9\u4f60\u627e\u5230\u6700\u4fbf\u5b9c\u7684\u641c\u7d22\u8bcd\uff1a  \n> \u8f93\u5165\u4f60\u60f3\u641c\u7d22\u7684\u5546\u54c1\u540d\uff0cAI \u4f1a\u7ed9\u51fa\u4f4e\u4ef7\u7684\u66ff\u4ee3\u54c1\uff0c\u7ed3\u679c\u53ef\u80fd\u4e0d\u51c6\uff0c\u5f00\u5fc3\u5c31\u597d :)  \n> \u7ecf\u6d4e\u5bd2\u51ac\uff0c\u5546\u54c1\u53ef\u4ee5\u5e73\u66ff\uff0c\u4f46\u4f60\u7684\u751f\u6d3b\u65e0\u6cd5\u88ab\u5e73\u66ff\u3002\n\n## \ud83d\udcbf \u5b89\u88c5\n\n\u4ee5\u4e0b\u63d0\u5230\u7684\u65b9\u6cd5 \u4efb\u9009**\u5176\u4e00** \u5373\u53ef\n\n<details open>\n<summary>[\u63a8\u8350] \u4f7f\u7528 nb-cli \u5b89\u88c5</summary>\n\u5728 nonebot2 \u9879\u76ee\u7684\u6839\u76ee\u5f55\u4e0b\u6253\u5f00\u547d\u4ee4\u884c, \u8f93\u5165\u4ee5\u4e0b\u6307\u4ee4\u5373\u53ef\u5b89\u88c5\n\n```bash\nnb plugin install nonebot-plugin-pingti\n```\n\n</details>\n\n<details>\n<summary>\u4f7f\u7528\u5305\u7ba1\u7406\u5668\u5b89\u88c5</summary>\n\u5728 nonebot2 \u9879\u76ee\u7684\u63d2\u4ef6\u76ee\u5f55\u4e0b, \u6253\u5f00\u547d\u4ee4\u884c, \u6839\u636e\u4f60\u4f7f\u7528\u7684\u5305\u7ba1\u7406\u5668, \u8f93\u5165\u76f8\u5e94\u7684\u5b89\u88c5\u547d\u4ee4\n\n<details>\n<summary>pip</summary>\n\n```bash\npip install nonebot-plugin-pingti\n```\n\n</details>\n<details>\n<summary>pdm</summary>\n\n```bash\npdm add nonebot-plugin-pingti\n```\n\n</details>\n<details>\n<summary>poetry</summary>\n\n```bash\npoetry add nonebot-plugin-pingti\n```\n\n</details>\n<details>\n<summary>conda</summary>\n\n```bash\nconda install nonebot-plugin-pingti\n```\n\n</details>\n\n\u6253\u5f00 nonebot2 \u9879\u76ee\u6839\u76ee\u5f55\u4e0b\u7684 `pyproject.toml` \u6587\u4ef6, \u5728 `[tool.nonebot]` \u90e8\u5206\u7684 `plugins` \u9879\u91cc\u8ffd\u52a0\u5199\u5165\n\n```toml\n[tool.nonebot]\nplugins = [\n    # ...\n    \"nonebot_plugin_pingti\"\n]\n```\n\n</details>\n\n## \u2699\ufe0f \u914d\u7f6e\n\n\u5728 NoneBot2 \u9879\u76ee\u7684`.env`\u6587\u4ef6\u4e2d\u6dfb\u52a0\u4e0b\u8868\u4e2d\u7684\u5fc5\u586b\u914d\u7f6e\n\n|           \u914d\u7f6e\u9879            | \u5fc5\u586b | \u9ed8\u8ba4\u503c  |            \u8bf4\u660e            |\n| :-------------------------: | :--: | :-----: | :------------------------: |\n|       `PINGTI_PROXY`        |  \u5426  |   \u65e0    |     \u8bf7\u6c42\u4f7f\u7528\u7684\u4ee3\u7406\u5730\u5740     |\n|  `PINGTI_REQUEST_TIMEOUT`   |  \u5426  |   `5`   |   \u8bf7\u6c42\u8d85\u65f6\u65f6\u95f4\uff0c\u5355\u4f4d\u4e3a\u79d2   |\n|      `PINGTI_SEND_TIP`      |  \u5426  | `True`  |      \u662f\u5426\u53d1\u9001\u63d0\u793a\u6d88\u606f      |\n|     `PINGTI_RECALL_TIP`     |  \u5426  | `True`  | \u53d1\u9001\u63d0\u793a\u6d88\u606f\u540e\u662f\u5426\u81ea\u52a8\u64a4\u56de |\n| `PINGTI_SHOW_ZERO_FEEDBACK` |  \u5426  | `False` |  \u662f\u5426\u5c55\u793a\u6570\u91cf\u4e3a 0 \u7684\u8bc4\u4ef7   |\n\n## \ud83c\udf89 \u4f7f\u7528\n\n\u6307\u4ee4\uff1a`\u5e73\u66ff`\n\n## \ud83d\udcde \u8054\u7cfb\n\nQQ\uff1a3076823485  \nTelegram\uff1a[@lgc2333](https://t.me/lgc2333)  \n\u5439\u6c34\u7fa4\uff1a[1105946125](https://jq.qq.com/?_wv=1027&k=Z3n1MpEp)  \n\u90ae\u7bb1\uff1a<lgc2333@126.com>\n\n## \ud83d\udca1 \u9e23\u8c22\n\n### [pingti.app](https://www.pingti.app/)\n\n- \u670d\u52a1\u63d0\u4f9b\n\n### [ilharp/koishi-plugin-pingti](https://github.com/ilharp/koishi-plugin-pingti)\n\n- ~~\u6284\u88ad~~ \u501f\u9274\n\n## \ud83d\udcb0 \u8d5e\u52a9\n\n**[\u8d5e\u52a9\u6211](https://blog.lgc2333.top/donate)**\n\n\u611f\u8c22\u5927\u5bb6\u7684\u8d5e\u52a9\uff01\u4f60\u4eec\u7684\u8d5e\u52a9\u5c06\u662f\u6211\u7ee7\u7eed\u521b\u4f5c\u7684\u52a8\u529b\uff01\n\n## \ud83d\udcdd \u66f4\u65b0\u65e5\u5fd7\n\n### 0.2.0\n\n- \u91cd\u6784\u63d2\u4ef6\n- \u65b0\u589e\u914d\u7f6e\u9879 `PINGTI_SHOW_ZERO_FEEDBACK`\n\n### 0.1.4\n\n- \u4fee\u590d [#2](https://github.com/lgc-NB2Dev/nonebot-plugin-pingti/issues/2)\n- \u517c\u5bb9 Pydantic V2\n\n### 0.1.3\n\n- \u4fee\u590d\u65e0\u6cd5\u4f7f\u7528\u7684\u95ee\u9898\n\n### 0.1.2\n\n- \u5b9e\u73b0 [#1](https://github.com/lgc-NB2Dev/nonebot-plugin-pingti/issues/1)\uff1a\n  - \u91cd\u547d\u540d\u914d\u7f6e\u9879 `PROXY` -> `PINGTI_PROXY`\n  - \u6dfb\u52a0\u914d\u7f6e\u9879 `PINGTI_SEND_TIP`\n  - \u6dfb\u52a0\u914d\u7f6e\u9879 `PINGTI_RECALL_TIP`\n\n### 0.1.1\n\n- \u4f18\u5316\u90e8\u5206\u903b\u8f91\n"], "modules": [{"name": "nonebot_plugin_pingti", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "nonebot_plugin_pingti.__version__", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "nonebot_plugin_pingti.__plugin_meta__", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "nonebot_plugin_pingti.OLD_DATA_DIR", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "nonebot_plugin_pingti.__main__", "xref": {"fqname": "nonebot_plugin_pingti..__main__", "project": null}}, {"name": "nonebot_plugin_pingti.ConfigModel", "xref": {"fqname": "nonebot_plugin_pingti.config.ConfigModel", "project": null}}, {"name": "nonebot_plugin_pingti.inherit_supported_adapters", "xref": {"fqname": "nonebot.plugin.inherit_supported_adapters", "project": "nonebot2"}}, {"nam